        <p class="MsoNormal"><span>A study has also been initiated to assess the impact of being interviewed and featured on Community Voices.&nbsp; We hypothesize that this experience may enhance the interviewees sense of connection to community, connectedness to nature, self-efficacy and self-reported conservation behavior.&nbsp; Surveys were conducted to assess baseline metrics prior to the interview for Community Voices.&nbsp; The dashboard team plans to conduct follow-up research within the next year to determine whether changes are evident in these psychological metrics.</span></p>
